        "translations": {
          "en": "Muhammad ibn al-Hasan ibn Ahmad ibn al-Walid (may Allah be pleased with him) narrated to us. He said: Muhammad ibn al-Hasan al-Saffar narrated to us, from Ayyub ibn Nuh, from Safwan ibn Yahya, from Hisham ibn Salim, from Abu Abdillah al-Sadiq (peace be upon him). He said: The Messenger of Allah (may Allah bless him and his family) said:",
